snippets.title: GameServerClustersService listGameServerClusters Sample
snippets.description: Lists game server clusters in a given project and location.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService getGameServerCluster Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single game server cluster.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService createGameServerCluster Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new game server cluster in a given project and location.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService previewCreateGameServerCluster Sample
snippets.description: Previews creation of a new game server cluster in a given project and location.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService deleteGameServerCluster Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a single game server cluster.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService previewDeleteGameServerCluster Sample
snippets.description: Previews deletion of a single game server cluster.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService updateGameServerCluster Sample

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService previewUpdateGameServerCluster Sample

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService listGameServerConfigs Sample
snippets.description: Lists game server configs in a given project, location, and game server deployment.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService getGameServerConfig Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single game server config.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService createGameServerConfig Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new game server config in a given project, location, and game server deployment. Game server configs are immutable, and are not applied until referenced in the game server deployment rollout resource.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService deleteGameServerConfig Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a single game server config. The deletion will fail if the game server config is referenced in a game server deployment rollout.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService listGameServerDeployments Sample
snippets.description: Lists game server deployments in a given project and location.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService getGameServerDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single game server deployment.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService createGameServerDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new game server deployment in a given project and location.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService deleteGameServerDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a single game server deployment.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService updateGameServerDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Patches a game server deployment.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService getGameServerDeploymentRollout Sample
snippets.description: Gets details a single game server deployment rollout.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService updateGameServerDeploymentRollout Sample
snippets.description: Patches a single game server deployment rollout. The method will not return an error if the update does not affect any existing realms. For example - if the default_game_server_config is changed but all existing realms use the override, that is valid. Similarly, if a non existing realm is explicitly called out in game_server_config_overrides field, that will also not result in an error.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService previewGameServerDeploymentRollout Sample
snippets.description: Previews the game server deployment rollout. This API does not mutate the rollout resource.

snippets.title: GameServerClustersService fetchDeploymentState Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves information about the current state of the game server deployment. Gathers all the Agones fleets and Agones autoscalers, including fleets running an older version of the game server deployment.
